            "deepseek:00734_12fecf531972fbcb:43bce959de1888b6",
            """
            * Active Peak Detector with Sample-Hold and Op-Amp Buffer
            VIN inp 0 SIN(2.5 2.5 1k)
            VOS in_pos inp DC 0.005
            Rin in_pos 0 1G
            E1 opamp_out 0 in_pos cap 100k
            Ccomp opamp_out 0 10pF
            R2 opamp_out nd_a 1k
