            "deepseek:01582_ca9507817fb9d1e1:fa0b794fbca2fcde",
            """
            * Op-amp sample-and-hold with ideal switch and leakage
            .OPTIONS POST
            VIN in 0 SIN(0 1 1k 0 0 0)
            VCTRL ctrl 0 PULSE(0 5 0 1n 1n 0.9m 10m)
            S1 in chold ctrl 0 sw1
            C1 chold 0 10n
